usic/watch-billie-eilish-join-green-day-for-last-night-on-earth-at-la-fireaid-concert-3833458">collaborating with the pop star at the recent FireAid benefit concert in LA</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-put-out-casting-call-for-punks-alts-hardcore-emo-and-rockers-for-new-movie-3839463">Green Day put out casting call for “punks, alts, hardcore, emo and rockers” for new movie</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
